1.0 Configuring 
###############
		./configure 

You may disable threads support by adding '--disable-threads'
i.e: "./configure --disable-threads".


1.1 Compiling
#############
		make clean
		make

1.2 Installing [optional]
#########################

		as root, execute 'make install'

For more information refer to the documentation section in ysmd's website.
[ http://ysmd.sourceforge.net ] 
